        Welcome to the Applicant Information Network Bulletin Board.


   General Instructions

      Grant Application

        Bulletin Board

   This site is for the use of parties who are interested in applying for
   grants from the Legal Services Corporation.  Information which
   applicants submit through this site is confidential and may not be
   distributed or discussed without the consent of the Legal Services
   Corporation and the applicant submitting the information.

   Click on Bulletin Board to access the LSC Request for Proposals and
   other information about applying for LSC grants.

                                  Your suggestions and comments about this
             site are appreciated. Please feel free to E-mail ain@lsc.gov.

